{{Use dmy dates|date=December 2015}} {{Infobox sportsperson | name = Joe Barral | birth_name = | fullname = | nickname = | nationality = | residence = | birth_date = {{birth date and age|1945|6|26|df=yes}} | birth_place = [[Monaco]] | death_date = | death_place = | height = | weight = | country = | sport = [[Shooting sport|Sports shooting]] | event = | medaltemplates = | show-medals = yes }}
'''Joe Barral''' (born 26 June 1945) is a [[Monaco|Monegasque]] former [[Shooting sport|sports shooter]]. He competed at the [[1968 Summer Olympics|1968]], [[1972 Summer Olympics|1972]] and the [[1976 Summer Olympics]].<ref name="SportsRef">{{cite web|url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ba/joe-barral-1.html |title=Joe Barral |accessdate=30 December 2015 |work=Sports Reference |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304042241/http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ba/joe-barral-1.html |archivedate= 4 March 2016 |df= }}</ref>
